item.title: Working At Branch
item.author: raravena80@gmail.com (Ricardo Aravena)
item.description: It has been about 4 months since I started working at Branch and wanted to reflect on what it’s been like. I can truly say that I’m enjoying everything about it. The environment is fantastic, my co-workers are awesome, and we all come from various backgrounds. I like the fact that the company takes their values seriously and the founding team is focused on making working at Branch the best experience you’ve ever had in your career.
